6. Read two numbers in (user input) and store as num1 and num2, Calculate the sum, difference, product, Quotient, reminder, power
num1 = float(input("first number: "))
num2= float(input("second number: "))

sum = num1 + num2
print(sum)

difference= num1 - num2
print(difference)

product= num1*num2
print(product)

Quotient= num1/num2
print(Quotient)

remainder= num1%num2
print(remainder)

power= num1**num2
print(power)

